          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-1">Fishbraai Thursday</h3>
          <p class="font-body text-amber-300/70 text-sm mb-4 flex-1">
            The homecoming session — deep log drum, smooth amapiano and pure township soul.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <a 
              href="https://wa.me/27432000000?text=Sawubona!%20I'd%20like%20to%20book%20for%20Fishbraai%20Thursday%20on%2018%20June" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="mt-5 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full py-2.5 rounded-xl border border-amber-400/20 bg-amber-400/5 font-body text-amber-300 text-sm hover:bg-amber-400/10 hover:border-amber-400/40 transition-all duration-200"
            >
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
